Package gov.nih.nlm.meme.xml

Provides all classes for XML parsing and generation for MEME documents.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
NotPersistentIfTransient Our XML serialization mechanism does not implicitly ignore transient information (because it causes problems with some JFC classes).
ObjectXMLSerializer.Primitive Anything implementing this method should also have a static newInstance(String) method.
XMLSerializer Generically represents a class that can convert objects to XML and back.
 

Class Summary
CGIStyleMEMEServiceRequest Represents a request made to the MEME server via the CGI interface.
MASRequestSerializer Used to map MEME service request documents to MEMEServiceRequest objects and vice-versa using the public MASRequestSerializer.fromXML(String) or MASRequestSerializer.fromXML(Reader), and MASRequestSerializer.toXML(Object) methods.
MedlineHandler SAX parser handler used to create intermediate data files from the Medline XML files.
MEMEServiceRequest Object form of the XML "MEME service request".
ObjectXMLSerializer Implements an XML serialization scheme for ANY java object.
Version History: 08/15/2005: Better handling of wrapper classes.
 

Package gov.nih.nlm.meme.xml Description

Provides all classes for XML parsing and generation for MEME documents.
